wiki.summary: "SHUM" (Ukrainian: Шум, transl. "Noise") is a song by Ukrainian electro-folk artist Go_A. It represented Ukraine in the Eurovision Song Contest 2021 in Rotterdam. The Eurovision version of the song took the lead in the global Spotify Viral 50 daily list on 24 May 2021, where it stayed until 1 June, and led the weekly list on the week of 27 May. It entered the Billboard Global 200 on the week of 5 June, at position 158, becoming the first ever Ukrainian language song to chart there. Read more on Last.fm.
